snippet.title: BATTLESHIP The Video Game | Official Activision Gameplay Trailer [HD]
snippet.description:
Pre-order Now at: http://battleshipthevideogame.com/

Discover why BATTLESHIP The Video Game is one of the most anticipated ACTIVISION game titles of 2012! Watch gameplay footage that brings you into the heart of battle both at sea and on land!  Available May 15th for Xbox 360, PlayStation 3, Nintendo Wii, Nintendo DS and Nintendo 3DS!
